name: HarryPotterObamaInu
description: What is HarryPotterObamaInu(INU)? HarryPotterObamaInu is the spellbindingly absurd world of magic, where Harry Potter meets Obama in a whirlwind of wackiness, and Shiba Inu take the stage as the ultimate financial advisors!Imagine a universe where magic spells and political speeches collide to create a currency that defies all logic and reason. Picture President Obama casting "Economicus Leviosanum" to lift the markets, while Harry Potter trades his wizarding gold for the latest HarryPotterObamaInu spells. HarryPotterObamaInu has a total supply of 1 billion tokens and operating on Ethereum Network. Embrace the uselessness and celebrate the hilarity of this memecoin phenomenon!
